      Supported Languages
    </div>
    <div class="whales__belugas__footer">
      Inside the Whales ecosystem, we have what we call Belugas.
      Belugas are analyzers dedicated to run feature detector
      engines on your local machine inside of Docker containers.
      <br/><br/>
      We currently support 4 languages: Java, Ruby, Python and Php,
      with more coming in the pipeline.
    </div>
  </div>

